1.0.0.name: wordpress/frame-free
1.0.0.description: Frame Free is a plugin to remove any frame created by Digg, Facebook, Google Images, Ow.ly and any other third party services. The plugin is inserting some Javascript in your HTML head section to remove the annoying frame such as DiggBar. Frame Free is brought to you by Chung Bey Luen.<br/> <br/> Plugin Homepage: Frame Free<br/>
